Tinah Priscilla Williams bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na-eje ozi dị ka onye otu North West Provincial Legislature kemgbe Mee 2019
Ọ na-anọchite anya African National Congress
Na June 2019, a họpụtara Williams dịka onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Portfolio na Social Development na Health.
Williams bụ onye otu African National Congress
A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu North West Provincial na ntuli aka 2019
Ọ malitere ọrụ dị ka onye otu na 22 Mee 2019.
N'ọnwa Juun afọ 2019, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi oche nke Kọmitii Portfolio na Social Development and Health.
Àtụ:Members of the North West Provincial Legislature
